'''Timothy M. Rose''' (born [[July]] [[July 17|17]], [[1950s|1956]]) is an American puppeteer best known for playing [[Admiral]] [[Gial Ackbar|Ackbar]] in [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']], [[Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens|''Star Wars'': Episode VII ''The Force Awakens'']] and [[Star Wars: Episode VIII The Last Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VIII ''The Last Jedi'']].

